headline: BofA sees share gains, record shipments ahead for Western Digital
summary: Investing.com -- Bank of America reiterated its Buy rating on Western Digital and raised its price target to $145 from $141 in a note, citing stronger-than-expected preliminary data for the company’s fiscal first quarter and signs of market share gains.

headline: 3 Inflated  Stocks with Questionable Fundamentals
summary: The stocks featured in this article are seeing some big returns. Over the past month, they’ve outpaced the market due to some combination of positive news, upbeat results, or supportive macro developments. As such, investors are taking notice and bidding up shares.
